<body>
<div type="letter">
 <pb facs="1037767" n="1"/> 
<opener><lb/><salute>Ad <rs type="person">Fratres Barlinckhofios</rs> <rs type="place">Groningam</rs>.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Non possum, Viri Juvenes doctissimi, Amici quondam charissimi, quin Vos per literas hasce ab <rs type="person">ancilla</rs>
    <lb/>nostra <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> reditum in <rs type="place">Patriam</rs> parat et iter suum Deo volente crastina die auspicabitur<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> Vobis per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ferendas interpellem, deque pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>senti rerum vestrarum statu interrogem. Non dubito Vos adhucdum
    <lb/>optime valere, et literas has meas pro sincero, quem erga me cum <rs type="place">Groning<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> degerem abunde testifica<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ti estis, affectu bono animo accepturos, nec <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gre laturos, quod Vobis impr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentiarum tot <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>utinam
    <lb/>plures fuissent<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> suaves quas una transegimus horas in memoriam revocem. Ego sane nescio quam
    <lb/>sentio voluptatem, dum h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c scribo, adeo me delectat antiqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> conversationis, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tam
    <lb/>longo temporis intervallo cessavit, memoria; et hora h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c, quam epistol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> huic scribend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> impendo,
    <lb/>quasi <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀνακεφαλαίωσις</foreign><note type="editorial" resp="SG">anakephalaiōsis. Begriff aus der Rhetorik. Gemeint ist eine zusammenfassende Wiederaufnahme der Hauptargumente bzw. Rekapitulation.</note> esse mihi videtur omnium illarum, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in illa conversatione effluxerunt,
    <lb/>et s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pe clam nobis instar servi fugitivi aufugerunt. Gratias proin Vobis etiamnum ago maximas
    <lb/>pro favore et benevolentia, qua me olim prosecuti estis, hanc qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so in posterum mihi conserva<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>te illibatam, quemadmodum et ego amicitiam vestram grata mente recolere nunquam cessabo.
    <lb/><abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Trip</rs>, <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-135875358">Gockinga</rs>, <rs type="person">Hoorn</rs> et <rs type="person">Swighu<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>sen</rs> in prospera sine dubio valetudine adhuc apud
    <lb/>Vos degunt, et forsan studia sua ad felicem perduxerunt metam, salutem illis meo nomine
    <lb/>dicatis oro, et quam magni faciam illorum nomina, quantique semper <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimaverim ipso<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum amicitiam illos per epistolam aliquam ipse fecissem certiores, nisi tempus me defe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cisset; gratissimum mihi certe erit, si comperero, illos hactenus de favore erga me suo nihil
    <lb/>remisisse. <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Basse</rs> sine dubio pro acumine suo magnus jam erit causarum Patronus, et
    <lb/>suum Schnip, Schnap, Schnorum, Basilorum dexterrime sciet ludere. Magnopere scire labo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ro, qualis sit <rs type="organisation">Academi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> status, quid pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> discessu nostro contigerit, annon
    <lb/>nov<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> turb<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> subinde exort<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint, annon novus surrexerit Mathematicus, cui bellum indicer<unclear reason="lost">e</unclear>
    <lb/>potuit egregius noster <rs type="person">Hulsius</rs>. Audivi illum post abitum nostrum, cum Rectoratum depo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>neret, recitasse meas et <rs type="person">Patrui</rs> mei <rs type="letter">literas</rs>, at <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> res indigna! imo <choice><orig><g ref="#ohat">ô</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> scelus indignum! itane neces<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sum fuit, ut <rs type="person">Heros</rs> noster <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>sciens absentes pro mortuis habere<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> mortuo Leoni evelleret
    <lb/>barbam? <del>[...]</del>Annon si se offensum putavit sese vindica<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>re potuit nobis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentibus? Sed ut audio non magnam ab Auditoribus reportavit 
    <pb facs="1037768" n="2"/> 
    <lb/>gratiam; quicquid sit quod exinde contigit rogo ut mihi scribatis, <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <abbr>Dn.</abbr> <rs type="person">Braunius</rs> li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>benter suis ad <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> meum <rs type="letter">literis</rs> includet. </p> <closer>Valete cum supra nominatis amicis et favere
      <lb/>pergite vestro <signed><rs type="person">NB.</rs></signed></closer>
</div>
